{"tid":695270,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有個靚女同我講加油，佢係咪中意我","createTime":"2018-06-09T05:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T08:03:50.000Z","uid":138919,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"06a4bbd7faa7dc9f222f1f26114a31b8b67fc4f7","tid":695270,"uid":138919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的，話說我係一間面包鋪做緊PT收銀仔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁今日都一如既往11點幾鳩fingfing咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，咁我咪攞部電話出黎玩Pokemon go囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係無啦啦係眼尾gup到有個靚女行緊入黎，仲要著住白色背心短裙仔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我個度係老人村<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以好少有靚女出入，咁好嘅機會我梗係唔會錯過啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我即刻放低部電話，扮抹下啲盤，希望短裙妹會留意到我啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後我再眼尾睄一睄佢，發現佢直望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑笑口咁攞左個菠蘿包過黎。雖然我冇咩拍拖經驗，但係呢一刻我就知我有機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我就幫短裙妹個包入袋啦，點知佢竟然同我講「加油呀」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我個刻真係好開心，竟然有女仔會同我講加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，真係咁大個仔第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我即刻回佢一句「你都加油呀」，但係個短裙妹個表情有啲錯愕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔通佢都係第一次有男仔同佢講加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最後佢連包都冇攞到就走左，唔知佢係咪緊張得濟呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98fdab46072c1323756ab9f7e07fae793b37512","tid":695270,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T05:10:15.000Z","msg":"是"},{"pid":"d04b2d6c7488d13e2fde0f62cce7ddaae2cc0f42","tid":695270,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T05:10:29.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"6e36041e9711dbeedf50cb5b56a400397bfc0de0","tid":695270,"uid":22449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T05:11:11.000Z","msg":"牛油 無咩創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a04d477f0e2afbe2594adc3f32e4deab3013ef3","tid":695270,"uid":138919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c98fdab46072c1323756ab9f7e07fae793b37512","tid":695270,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T05:10:15.000Z","msg":"是"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T05:12:01.000Z","msg":"我都係咁覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd217440eb976c2ca43a8bbb67f1af75230ff1c","tid":695270,"uid":44454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"你都係想講個靚女想要菠蘿油姐，打咁大篇野唔好笑囉"},{"pid":"c4914a97566c0f4842395cef205416818c57f814","tid":695270,"uid":138919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e36041e9711dbeedf50cb5b56a400397bfc0de0","tid":695270,"uid":22449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T05:11:11.000Z","msg":"牛油 無咩創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T05:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a6204fd777bdd93fae975f80e67f3e90bfac7b","tid":695270,"uid":138919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bd217440eb976c2ca43a8bbb67f1af75230ff1c","tid":695270,"uid":44454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"你都係想講個靚女想要菠蘿油姐，打咁大篇野唔好笑囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T05:16:40.000Z","m